\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 WE
\f1\b0\fs24 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Today I want us to look at a phenomenon called Cognitive Dissonance. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 Cognitive Dissonance is the state of having inconsistent thoughts, beliefs, or attitudes, especially as relating to behavioral decisions and attitude change. \'a0\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
This is a fancy way of saying a persons beliefs don\'92t line up with their behaviors. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
And this happens all the time in our lives.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
I believe eating healthy is a great choice\'85but I choose McDonalds fries.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
I believe that saving money for my futures is the best choice\'85but I really want to buy some new shoes. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
I believe (need a few more examples here)\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
But this Dissonance happens in more areas than those...\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
They happen in the church also.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Where people sign up for faith in God, they sign up to give their lives Christ because a pastor says just pray this prayer.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
They ask a question - do you want a better life? \'a0Then just pray this prayer.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
They check the box on the card - I want a better life\'85I agree to the Terms and Conditions.\'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Often times not truly understanding what those terms and conditions are\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Which causes the Cognitive Dissonance.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Because now they have a new set of beliefs but no behaviors to back them up.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
This explains why so many of you are frustrated with your life or maybe even God.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Because you signed up for something and there are expectations God has of you and you agreed to\'85but haven\'92t really thought through the disconnects yet. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
This also explains maybe why some of you are struggling to put your faith in Christ because you see how His supposed people behave\'85and you think to yourself\'85they say one thing but behave differently\'85I don\'92t need that in my life. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
And so today\'85I want to walk through what a person actually signs up for and what it means to be a follower of Jesus.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
What is the process and where are the disconnects.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
